Package sndlib.core.util

Class Summary
DateFormat This class encapsulates the common date format of SNDlib.
DoubleComparator This class defines an epsilon for floating point comparisons in SNDlib.
DoubleFormat This class encapsulates the common format for double numbers in SNDlib.
MaximumLinkFlow This is a simple class containing the maximum flows on a specific link, together with the states in which the flow values are assumed.
NamingConventions This class provides methods to construct the conventional names of Problems and Models in SNDlib.
NetworkUtils This class provides some commonly used utility methods on a Network (or rather a Problem).
PathSet This class represents a set containing pairwise different paths.
PathSet.PathComparator Compares the paths with respect to a specific link model.
SNDlibMessages This class provides a static interface for creating keyed messages used in SNDlib, e.g. the IO implementation.
SolutionUtils This class provides some commonly used utility methods on a Solution (resp. a SolvedProblem).
